===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|locuste}}, {{m|enm|locust}}, from {{der|en|xno|locuste}}, {{der|en|frm|locuste}}, and their source, {{der|en|la|locusta||locust, crustacean, lobster}}.<ref>{{R:OED Online|code=109676}}</ref> {{doublet|en|langouste}}. The sense in "Mainlander" directly borrows {{bor|en|zh|蝗蟲}} (wong4 cung4), also meaning "locust".

