===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Any of the [[grasshopper]]s, often [[polyphenic]] and usually [[swarming]], in the family [[Acrididae]] that are very [[destructive]] to [[crop]]s and other [[vegetation]], {{i|especially}} the {{vern|migratory locust}} ({{taxlink|Locusta migratoria|species|noshow=1|ver=161006}}). {{defdate|from 14th c.}}
# {{lb|en|now|historical}} A fruit or [[pod]] of the [[carob tree]]. {{defdate|from 16th c.}}
#*'''1789''', {{w|Olaudah Equiano}}, ''The Interesting Narrative'', vol. I, ch. 9:
#*:Among other articles, they brought with them a great quantity of '''locusts''', which are a kind of pulse, sweet and pleasant to the palate, and in shape resembling French beans, but longer.
# Any of various often [[leguminous]] trees and shrubs, especially of the genera ''[[Robinia]]'' and ''[[Gleditsia]]''; the [[locust tree]]. {{defdate|from 17th c.}}
# A [[cicada]]. {{defdate|from 18th c.}}
# {{lb|en|Hong Kong|derogatory|offensive}} A [[Mainlander]].

